The following .R files should be run in order

step 1:
mkdata.R  generate simulation data

step 2:
run.R   run linear mixed-effect models or linear regression models for the three models DNA+Taxa, DNA, and Taxa

step 3:
perf.R  get statitical power and AUC performances

step 4:
plot.R  plot statitical power and AUC performances

step 5:
fdr.R  plot real FDR at 0.05 nominal FDR
